{"tid":417351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港航跪低！涉無理解僱空少","createTime":"2017-09-28T14:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T22:50:06.000Z","uid":69930,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"54dbfb6b3c5a3cd70b585cc2301984b6df61aa14","tid":417351,"uid":69930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港航空一名空少，早前要求一名醉酒乘客下機，但該乘客疑是公司高層朋友，空少最終遭無故解僱</strong></span></span>，事件引起公眾關注。<br />\n<br />\n港航近日改變主意，今日向員工發電郵稱公司決定繼續聘用涉事空少，<br />\n即時生效，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但並無問責</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170928/57268052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170928%2F57268052&d=wBeSCwnTTd5wjbNQPqXIAP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=cc313926\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170928%2F57268052&h=114b28a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170928/57268052</a><br />\n<br />\n2011年12月13日上海A股上市的<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">海南航空</span></strong></span>股份全資子公司海南航空（香港）公司的全資子公司Hainan Airlines Investment Holding Co. Limited<br />\n以總價8.42億人民幣（10億港元）、<br />\n注資香港航空，<br />\n注資後持有香港航空19.02％股權。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA&d=wBeSCwnTTd5wjbNQPqXIAP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9550f407\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA</a></span>"},{"pid":"045c52d5f1dd2282af764a3b7da72cc9bd41820d","tid":417351,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09